        <h5 class="card-title">Petstop Sofa Bed Chenille Aqua</h5>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card hover-shadow">
      <%= link_to image_tag('go_native_chicken.png', class: "img"), controller: 'products', action: 'show', id: 5 %>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Red Mills - Go Native - Chicken</h5>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <!--Card-->

  <h1 class="text-center my-5 font-weight-bold">ABOUT US<hr></h1>

  <div class="row">

    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
      <p>We are a chain of pet stores in Ireland, stocking a range of pet food brands,
        supplies, accessories and so much more to fit all of your pet care requirements.
        With three large pet superstores in Dublin (Blanchardstown, Swords & Carrickmines),
        one in Naas, Co. Kildare, one in Cork, one in Tralee, Kerry and our newest one in Limerick.
        We are dedicated to providing you with the best products and services for your pet.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
      <p>We are passionate about pets, stocking over 7,000 products for all kinds of pets online,
        at great prices with fast and convenient delivery all over Ireland. At Pet Stop you will
        find a great range of products for all kinds of pets, from small pets including hamsters,
        rabbits and gerbils, to dogs, cats, reptiles, birds, wild birds, fish and more. Our friendly,
        qualified staff are on hand to offer health advice, and products to keep your pet healthy
        and happy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
      <p>Whether you are looking for specific dog food, cat food, or toy and accessory to keep
        your pet healthy and happy, we stock everything you need so you can kit your home,
        garden and even car out; from collars, toys and treats to kennels, cages,
        leads and so much more, Petstop is your one stop shop for all your pet care needs.
        We are always here to help.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
